Body: Thank you for your support!  to answer your question - we at PlaceToRent will strive to engineer responsible social behavior of our users on the platform with AI and data. For this purpose, our user performance/reputation rating system will become an official recognition of all the data on the PlaceToRent users collected and circulating and will impact them in a multitude of ways. Anything that influences our users points will be backed by official documents and immutable transactions recorded on the blockchain.  How the users negotiate their social conduct on the platform will be directly proportionate to their performance/reputation scores that will reflect not only on their chances to access certain services and privileges, but on the social contracts we embark on with the whole ecosystem at large.  PLACETORENT
